title: Daniel Jones replaces Eli Manning as Giants starting QB (Football 9/18)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn and Ryan Wilson to discuss the Giants decision to replace Eli Manning with Daniel Jones (1:30). The guys also analyze player empowerment in the NFL (24:00) , the impact of Cam Newton's aggravated injury (31:00), and 0-2 teams that could still make the playoffs (36:00) before dissecting Pete Prisco's Power Rankings (49:00).
